<codeline><highlight class="normal">#<sp/>AtlasRenderer<sp/>분석</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">##<sp/>목적</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">이<sp/>문서의<sp/>목적은<sp/>`AtlasRenderer`가<sp/>실제<sp/>렌더링에<sp/>필요로<sp/>하는<sp/>최소<sp/>데이터를<sp/>식별하고,<sp/>`TextVisualizer`가<sp/>기존<sp/>`Text::Controller`<sp/>전체에<sp/>의존하지<sp/>않고도<sp/>`AtlasRenderer`를<sp/>직접<sp/>사용할<sp/>수<sp/>있는지<sp/>검토하는<sp/>것이다.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">특히<sp/>아래를<sp/>명확히<sp/>정리한다.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>`AtlasRenderer`<sp/>생성<sp/>방식</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>public/internal<sp/>API<sp/>구조</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>`Render()`<sp/>호출<sp/>흐름</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>현재<sp/>controller/view/model로부터<sp/>가져오는<sp/>데이터<sp/>목록</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>실제<sp/>최소<sp/>glyph<sp/>/<sp/>layout<sp/>데이터</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>style<sp/>/<sp/>ellipsis<sp/>/<sp/>selection<sp/>없이<sp/>필요한<sp/>최소<sp/>렌더링<sp/>계약</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>`TextVisualizer`용<sp/>adapter<sp/>/<sp/>interface<sp/>설계<sp/>방향</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>기존<sp/>`AtlasRenderer`<sp/>수정<sp/>필요<sp/>여부와<sp/>최소<sp/>변경<sp/>방향</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">애매한<sp/>내용은<sp/>추측하지<sp/>않고<sp/>`확인<sp/>필요`로<sp/>표시한다.</highlight></codeline>
