<codeline><highlight class="normal">##<sp/>Render<sp/>호출<sp/>흐름</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">###<sp/>관련<sp/>함수</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>`AtlasRenderer::Render(...)`</highlight></codeline>
