<codeline><highlight class="normal">|<sp/>shadow<sp/>offset/color<sp/>|<sp/>`VisualModel`<sp/>|<sp/>zero<sp/>값<sp/>반환<sp/>adapter<sp/>|<sp/>1차<sp/>구현<sp/>비필수<sp/>|</highlight></codeline>
