<codeline><highlight class="normal">|<sp/>strikethrough<sp/>runs<sp/>/<sp/>style<sp/>|<sp/>`VisualModel`<sp/>|<sp/>disabled<sp/>/<sp/>empty<sp/>반환<sp/>adapter<sp/>|<sp/>1차<sp/>구현<sp/>비필수<sp/>|</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">|<sp/>outline<sp/>width/color/offset<sp/>|<sp/>`VisualModel`<sp/>|<sp/>zero<sp/>값<sp/>반환<sp/>adapter<sp/>|<sp/>1차<sp/>구현<sp/>비필수<sp/>|</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">|<sp/>hyphen<sp/>glyph/index/count<sp/>|<sp/>`VisualModel`<sp/>|<sp/>null<sp/>/<sp/>0<sp/>반환<sp/>adapter<sp/>|<sp/>1차<sp/>구현<sp/>비필수<sp/>|</highlight></codeline>
